Text.val: ////1999.1.13 ENGINE CALCURATE MODIFY VQ->AF BASE BY ASKA

SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT 0 , COUNT (*) FROM PRD007 UNION SELECT 1 , COUNT (*) FROM PRD007 WHERE PRD007.PRD_DAT = ':1' UNION SELECT 2 , COUNT (*) FROM PRD007 WHERE PRD007.PRD_DAT = ':2'

SELECT P7.PRD_DAT, P7.MTOCD, P7.COL_CD, P7.COLI_CD, P7.PRD_LIN, P7.EFM, P7.PRGRES, P7.M_AFPLN, P7.M_AFOFF, P7.M_VQOFF, P7.M_PAKING, P7.M_SHPNG, P7.M_RTN, P7.M_RSHPNG, P7.M_EXOUT, P7.STK_NVQ, P7.STK_VQ, P7.STK_PAK, P1.MTONAM, P1.CTEGRY, P1.OEM_CAT FROM PRD007 P7, PRD001 P1 WHERE P7.PRD_DAT = ':1' AND P1.MTOCD = P7.MTOCD AND (P7.PRGRES<>0 OR P7.M_AFPLN<>0 OR P7.M_AFOFF<>0 OR P7.M_VQOFF<>0 OR P7.M_PAKING<>0 OR P7.M_SHPNG<>0 OR P7.M_RTN<>0 OR P7.M_RSHPNG<>0 OR P7.M_EXOUT<>0 OR P7.STK_NVQ<>0 OR P7.STK_VQ<>0 OR P7.STK_PAK<>0) ORDER BY P7.EFM, P7.PRD_LIN, P1.CTEGRY, P7.MTOCD, P7.COL_CD, P7.COLI_CD
